  "text": "Drugs were applied to hippocampal cultures via bath superfusion using a three-way tap system. For serotonin (5-HT) and norepinephrine (NE) (Tocris), particular care was taken to minimize compound oxidation [CITATION_1] . A stock in distilled water was made immediately before the experiment and added to the bath solution to reach the final concentration.",
